          "title": "About the Course",
          "entries": [
            {
              "title": "About the Course",
              "content": "This course includes the following topic(s): Playground Games, Sports, Free Play/ Circuits, Folk Dancing\n\nAbout Folk Dancing\nLearn basic steps for individual, couple, and/or group dances using traditional folk songs.\n\nAbout Playground Games\nPlay group playground games.\n\nAbout Sports\nThis year, students will learn how to play football, badminton, and softball through participating in a variety of games, skills, and activities. Activities are geared for smaller groups of students but can be adjusted to any size.\n\nAbout Free Play/ Circuits\nMake fitness-building routines a habit.\n\nPE: Grades 4-6\nLessons specifically created for Grades 1-6. We recommend you make sure to include some sort of physical activity as breaks throughout your school day. If you already have sports or similar activities as a regular part of your life rhythms, these lessons are optional."
            }
          ]
        },
